name: End of Duty
description:
You are a simple worker on a space station. After a hard day's work, you want to return home as soon as possible, but for this you need to leave your equipment in its proper places.

Controls:
A - move left
D - move right
W - jump
C - use chainsaw
R - restart level
M - mute the music

Developers:
Jet1902
Zexis

How to launch:
- Download ZIP
- Launch End of Duty.exe
